{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/eww.png?t=1739361656\" />  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What is The Enigma Case?\u00a0\ud83d\udd75\ufe0f\u200d\u2642\ufe0f</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Enigma Cases will test your detective abilities, drawing you into complex and detailed cases. Examine crime scenes, gather and analyze clues, interrogate suspects, and take all necessary steps to solve the cases. Each case offers a different challenge and mystery to solve. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/UntitledProject-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1739361656\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Varied Cases</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Murders, Accidents, and Suicides: Each case has a unique story and mysteries waiting to be solved. Use all your detective skills to solve murders, accidents, and suicides. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Realistic Crime Scenes: Examine crime scenes in detail. From cafes to highways, every location is carefully designed and filled with clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/hackpc.gif?t=1739361656\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Detective Roles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Field Detective: Collects physical evidence at the crime scene, analyzes the clues, and interrogates suspects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cyber Detective: Investigates digital evidence, examines social media accounts, and analyzes emails and GPS records.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/ezgif-4-5b3477cd3b.gif?t=1739361656\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Multiplayer Cooperation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with Friends: Work together with your friends to solve cases. Each player can take on a different role, collaborating to uncover the truth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Online Community: Join forces with other detectives, share clues, and solve the toughest cases together. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/pc-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1739361656\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">In-Depth Investigations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Security Cameras and Digital Evidence: Examine security camera footage at the crime scene, gather and analyze digital evidence. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Toxicological and Forensic Examinations: Determine the cause of death in poisoning cases by using autopsy reports and toxicological analyses. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Realistic and Engaging Stories</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Detailed Scenarios: Each case offers a detailed and realistic story that will draw you in. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Surprising Outcomes: Be prepared for surprises and unexpected outcomes at the end of each case.<br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Add to Your Wish List</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please add our game to your wishlist and join our Discord to support us in development!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/extras/wishlist.gif?t=1739361656\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739361656","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739361656","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062170/068ffdc2ea2c3b9cf0a2536e914898bd3f8ee8fa/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739361656","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/306